    {
      "chinese": "聚會所、房屋、瞭望台、牛舍、倉庫、廚房都就地取材，用什麼木材為柱為樑？用什麼竹子為牆為房頂？怎麼用藤條綁住才牢固？這些都是當時部落男子重要的學習課題之一。這些都是我們要學習的袓先的智慧。",
      "ab": "U taluan nu niyaru’, luma’, pisevengan, pararapaan, alili, aniva nu Pangcah, u kilang, u aul, u ’eli atu uway ku sapatireng. U nisimsiman a mikilim tu papilian, u punuh nu tuas kiniyan. U maanan a kilang ku salilian? U maan a aulan ku sapavaduwac? Maanen ku nipiluec tu uway, ta makelec a tanektek saw? Iniyan i tangal amin nu matuasay. U nananaman nu mita u vavainayan. Akaa kapawan kita, malasawadaw ku punuh nu tuas.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2020/12/17/03190309cbcd7161a426abd4782bdcd2.wav",
